---
import '../styles/why.css';
---
<section class="why paper-tex paper-tex-warm" id="why">
  <div class="why-inner">
    <div class="why-top">
      <h2 class="r">Economic impact and policy analysis are strategic tools that pay for themselves</h2>
      <div class="why-top-right">
        <p class="r d1">Economic impact and policy analysis measures how an organization's spending, hiring, and operations ripple through a regional economy — and how policy decisions shape who benefits. It turns budgets, programs, and policy alternatives into a clear map of consequences.</p>
        <div class="why-diff r d2">Traditional tools rely on modeled estimates and outdated national averages that are only updated every few years. Lumecon applies rigorous methods to administrative and high-frequency data — so your results reflect your economy, not a generic assumption.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="why-cards r d2">
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-card-front">
          <div class="why-card-geo"><svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><path d="M12 34L22 10L32 34" stroke="#C49A3C" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none"/><path d="M8 38L22 14L36 38" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width=".8" opacity=".35" fill="none"/><line x1="16" y1="26" x2="28" y2="26" stroke="#B85C38" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="14" y1="30" x2="30" y2="30" stroke="#B85C38" stroke-width=".8" opacity=".5"/><circle cx="22" cy="10" r="3" stroke="#C49A3C" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/><circle cx="22" cy="10" r="1.2" fill="#C49A3C"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Secure funding</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card-back"><p>Show funders, councils, and legislators exactly what your organization contributes. Impact numbers turn budget conversations into investment conversations.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-card-front">
          <div class="why-card-geo"><svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><rect x="5" y="5" width="34" height="34" stroke="#C49A3C" stroke-width="1" rx="1"/><path d="M5 22h34" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width=".7" opacity=".4"/><path d="M22 5v34" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width=".7" opacity=".4"/><path d="M10 34L17 22 24 28 36 12" stroke="#B85C38" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M10 10L17 28 24 20 36 34" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Compare scenarios</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card-back"><p>What happens if you cut a program? Add 20 positions? Expand operations? Change a policy? Model the economic consequences of strategic decisions before you commit the resources.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-card-front">
          <div class="why-card-geo"><svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="4" fill="#C49A3C" opacity=".5"/><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="4" stroke="#C49A3C" stroke-width="1.2"/><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="10" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1" opacity=".6"/><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="17" stroke="#B85C38" stroke-width=".8" opacity=".35"/><line x1="22" y1="5" x2="22" y2="12" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="22" y1="32" x2="22" y2="39" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="5" y1="22" x2="12" y2="22" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="32" y1="22" x2="39" y2="22" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="10" y1="10" x2="14.5" y2="14.5" stroke="#B85C38" stroke-width=".8" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="29.5" y1="29.5" x2="34" y2="34" stroke="#B85C38" stroke-width=".8" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Streamline compliance</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card-back"><p>Federal grants, foundation reporting, and regulatory reviews often require the same economic data. Generate compliance-ready outputs from analysis you're already running.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-card-front">
          <div class="why-card-geo"><svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><rect x="10" y="14" width="20" height="24" rx="1.5" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width=".8" opacity=".3"/><rect x="8" y="10" width="20" height="24" rx="1.5" stroke="#B85C38" stroke-width=".8" opacity=".5"/><rect x="6" y="6" width="20" height="24" rx="1.5" stroke="#C49A3C" stroke-width="1.2" fill="var(--white)" fill-opacity=".4"/><line x1="10" y1="13" x2="22" y2="13" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="10" y1="17" x2="19" y2="17" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width=".8" stroke-linecap="round" opacity=".5"/><line x1="10" y1="21" x2="21" y2="21" stroke="#B85C38" stroke-width=".8" stroke-linecap="round" opacity=".4"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Tell your story</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card-back"><p>Annual reports, press releases, community presentations. Impact data makes the case in language stakeholders understand — people supported, dollars circulated.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
